-- Chavez Says Citic to ‘Participate’ in Petropiar Oil Venture
-- B y   N a t h a n   C r o o k s
-- 2012-02-24T19:34:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-24/chavez-says-citic-to-participate-in-petropiar-oil-venture.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez 
said that  China ’s Citic Group Corp. will sign an agreement to
“participate” in the Petropiar oil venture with Petroleos de
Venezuela SA and Chevron Corp on Feb. 27.  Chavez, speaking today in a nationwide broadcast, didn’t
provide any additional details. Chevron has a minority stake in
the venture.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nathan Crooks in Caracas at 
 ncrooks@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net  